OL,3,CNew Order's Peter Hook pays tribute to
OL,4,Clandlord of iconic pub after sudden
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FMembers of Manchester's music scene
OL,8,Ftribute to a father-of-two who ran an
OL,9,Fwell known pub before his sudden death.
OL,11,FAndy Martin, 52, was the landlord of
OL,12,FThe Star and Garter in for 21 years.
OL,13,FOn Friday 29 March, he suffered a
OL,14,Fsuspected stroke which led to sepsis
OL,15,Fand meningitis.
OL,17,FUp until his death, Andy ran the Grade
OL,18,FII-listed pub on Fairfield Street,
OL,19,FArdwick, with his work widely
OL,20,Frecognised as crucial to ensuring the
OL,21,Ffamed pub survived in difficult times.
