OL,7,FHelen, 41, said her husband became
OL,8,Funwell with a virus while on holiday
OL,9,Fin north Wales.
OL,11,FAfter returning home, Andy told his
OL,12,Fwife he was "freezing cold" despite
OL,13,Fhaving a high temperature.
OL,15,FHelen said: "On the way home I said:
OL,16,F'Do you think you should go to A&E?'
OL,17,FHe said: 'I'll be fine, I'll ring the
OL,18,Fdoctors first thing tomorrow'.
