OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"We got home and he said he wanted to
OL,8,Fsleep downstairs in front of the fire
OL,9,Fbecause he was so cold."
OL,11,FOn 25 March, Helen woke up to find her
OL,12,Fhusband, who she married last October,
OL,13,Fsitting in the bathroom.
OL,15,FShe said: "He was just looking at me
OL,16,Fand not speaking.J"I said: 'What's
OL,17,Fwrong? What's wrong?' I was worried.
OL,18,FHe said he just felt really sick. He
OL,19,Fmanaged to go into the bedroom, he was
OL,20,Fconscious but he wasn't able to speak
OL,21,Fto me."
