OL,7,FNew Order bassist Mr Hook has been a
OL,8,Fregular at The Star and Garter, as he
OL,9,Fprepares to perform a special charity
OL,10,Fgig of Joy Division classics in aid of
OL,11,Fmental health charities at the venue
OL,12,Fin April.
