OL,7,FMr Hook said: "Andy was a lovely man
OL,8,Ffrom head to foot. Truly a man of the
OL,9,Fpeople who recognised that mighty oaks
OL,10,Fgrow from acorns. His importance to
OL,11,Fnew Manchester music was vital. God
OL,12,Frest his soul."JSalford Lads Club
OL,13,Fposted on X: "We're sad to hear this
OL,14,Fnews - Andy was a key figure in
OL,15,FManchester's music community. Our
OL,16,Fthoughts are with his family."JSacha
OL,17,FLord, co-creator of and The Warehouse
OL,18,FProject clubnight, added: "I'm
OL,19,Fextremely saddened to hear the news
OL,20,Fthat Andy Martin from the Star and
OL,21,FGarter has passed away. We were only
OL,22,Fmessaging a couple of weeks ago.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/12
