OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"He was so soft with those children.
OL,8,FIt just melted him and it gave him
OL,9,Fsuch purpose in life."
OL,11,FThe timing of Mr Martin's death, on
OL,12,Fthe Easter bank holiday weekend, meant
OL,13,Fthat his wife was unable to sort out
OL,14,Ffinances for The Star and Garter for a
OL,15,Ffew days. In the short term, Ms
OL,16,FKitchen intends for another member of
OL,17,Fthe pub's team to take on the licence.
