OL,7,FOn longer term plans, Helen, who works
OL,8,Fas an office manager for a medical
OL,9,Fcompany, said: "I think Andy would
OL,10,Fwant someone to buy the business - but
OL,11,Fsomeone that would love it, keep the
OL,12,Fsame staff on, and keep the same vibe.
OL,13,FIn the next couple of months I will be
OL,14,Ftrying to take steps for that."
OL,16,FShe said the outpouring of love and
OL,17,Ftributes from the city's music scene
OL,18,Fhad been 'incredibly comforting'.
